channel.title: Status Page?
channel.description: Not really sure if this is the right section, probly isnt but it seems like the best one to put this in. Why does my server ALWAYS get deleted? Ive tryed 5 different ips, my server used to be like always near the top or always on, now it gets deleted within a couple minutes when it gets put on. YES, my server is UP 24/7 VPS, ill even put it on the status page, and 100% sure my server is up the whole time. My ips are: Hunt3rscape.no-ip.biz, Hunterpvp.no-ip.biz, hunterscape.servebeer.com, pkerzdream.no-ip.biz, and squirrelscape.no-ip.biz Any help?
